    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would best suit someone looking for a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including several large dents and noticeable rust patches, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Mechanically, it requires immediate attention as it currently runs roughly and will need significant repairs to be considered roadworthy. While it has served its purpose in the past, it is priced to reflect the extensive work required to restore it to a reliable state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
