    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a showroom-grade example with flawless aesthetics and mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a legacy of uncompromising care. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-quality motorcar.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see this beauty go to a great home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD) in an unmolested, factory-original configuration. This specimen features the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting perfect compression and a seamless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos. The chassis is a marvel of 50/50 weight distribution, supported by its original four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a functional Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line, solenoid, and heat shield is intact, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule and climate-controlled storage. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cockpit remains free of the typical UV-induced brittle plastics or bolster wear. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an apex-level JDM icon with total mechanical transparency.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Maintenance records included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Every switch, dial, and digital interface operates with factory-new precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented in a comprehensive service binder. The undercarriage is equally pristine, showing no signs of road debris or oxidation. This car drives with the tight, responsive feel of a brand-new vehicle, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, reflecting a standard of care that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, adheres strictly to original factory specifications. Mechanically superior and aesthetically peerless, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in showroom state. We invite serious inquiries for this distinguished asset.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and drives like a total dream. If you've been looking for that perfect ride that looks and feels brand new, you\u2019ve definitely found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how special this car is!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen boasts impeccable mechanical integrity with the 'Big Three' already addressed: rod bearings replaced, VANOS system overhauled with upgraded components, and the rear subframe reinforced. The atmospheric induction through individual throttle bodies remains crisp, delivering linear power to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis preserves its original rigidity, and the suspension geometry is dialed for precision. This is a turn-key, preservation-quality example with zero deferred maintenance and documented service history.",
